'''Bruce Spence''' (born [[September 17]], [[1940s#1945|1945]]<ref name="This Week Mandalorian Trailer" />) is a New Zealand-Australian actor, who portrayed [[Tion Medon]], a [[Port Administrator]], in [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']].<ref name="III">{{Film|III}}</ref> He has a large fan base due to his participation in various film franchises such as [[Wikipedia:Mad Max (franchise)|''Mad Max'']], [[Wikipedia:The Matrix (franchise)|''Matrix'']] and [[Wikipedia:The Lord of the Rings film trilogy|''Lord of the Rings'']].

